==Tatar==
===Etymology===
Romanized variant of [[хар]]. Middle Tatar (tatarcha), 1524 - 1669 year. Akin to English [[hoar#English|hoar]].

===Noun===
'''har'''
#[[hoar]] [[frost]], [[snow]]

